":"included image","folgerObjectType":"image","label":"leaf 2 verso","mpso":756,"description":"digital image"}]}
2144	c679fca8-5e86-490e-b278-1ad670dd1203	2017-08-16 16:50:54	2017-08-16 16:50:54	08048aad-e26e-4673-a34f-0ca98233d87c	1	1	{"RemoteUniqueID":"http:\\/\\/findingaids.folger.edu\\/dfobagot.xml#La272","name":"Letter from Richard Broughton (Richard Bagot's son-in-law) to Richard Bagot","dateCreated":"1593 May 26","description":"The plague growing worse, the next term to be adjourned. Wants Humphrey to bring the horses about June 15; hopes to be at Blithfield about June 29. Lady Rich wants Anne Broughton at Lees, where Lady Rich's mother and sister Dorothy are to be. The Staffordshire privy seals will not be repaid before Michaelmas. Discusses Bagot's claim for reimbursement of money laid out at Beaudesert; Sir Amias Paulet, Mr. Auditor Conyers, and others are mentioned. The Court is at Nonsuch; to be at Oatlands (Otelands) next.","folgerCallNumber":"L.a.272","format":"text","folgerGenre":"letters","agent":[{"name":"Richard Broughton (Richard Bagot's son-in-law)","description":"creator"},{"name":"Richard Bagot","description":"recipient"}],"inLanguage":"eng","folgerRelatedItems":[{"@id":"DAP internal ID for the following rootfile","folgerRemoteIdentification":{"folgerRemoteUniqueID":"39509","folgerRemoteSystemID":"luna"},"folgerRelationshipType":"included image","folgerObjectType":"image","label":"leaf 1 recto","mpso":757,"description":"digital image"},{"@id":"DAP internal ID for the following rootfile","folgerRemoteIdentification":{"folgerRemoteUniqueID":"39510","folgerRemoteSystemID":"luna"},"folgerRelationshipType":"included image","folgerObjectType":"image","label":"leaf 1 verso","mpso":758,"description":"digital image"},{"@id":"DAP internal ID for the following rootfile","folgerRemoteIdentification":{"folgerRemoteUniqueID":"39511","folgerRemoteSystemID":"luna"},"folgerRelationshipType":"included image","folgerObjectType":"image","label":"leaf 2 recto","mpso":759,"description":"digital image"},{"@id":"DAP internal ID for the following rootfile","folgerRemoteIdentifica